Description: Sets the Proton GE release build to install. If "Specific version" is selected, the version must be set under Specific Proton GE Release Version. Update the server after changing this setting

Sets the [release version](https://github.com/GloriousEggroll/proton-ge-custom/releases) for a specific Proton GE release build to install, if "Specific version" is selected under Proton GE Release. Example: GE-Proton9-1
